{"title_page": "Eluveitie discography", "text_new": "{{Infobox artist discography\n| Artist       = Eluveitie\n| Studio       = 8\n| Live         = 1\n| Compilation  = 2\n| Music videos = 11\n| EP           = 1\n| Singles      = 9\n}}\n'''[[Eluveitie]]''' ({{IPAc-en|\u025b|l|\u02c8|v|e\u026a|t|i}} {{respell|el|VAY|ti}})<ref name=\"metalist.co.il\">{{cite web|url=http://www.metalist.co.il/InterviewPrivate.asp?id=291&lang=eng|title=:: Metalist Magazine :: Interviews :: Eluveitie - \u05d4\u05d2\u05dc \u05d4\u05d7\u05d3\u05e9 \u05e9\u05dc \u05d4\u05e4\u05d5\u05dc\u05e7 \u05de\u05d8\u05d0\u05dc ::|website=www.metalist.co.il}}</ref> is a Swiss [[folk metal]] band from [[Winterthur]], [[Canton of Z\u00fcrich|Z\u00fcrich]] founded by [[Chrigel Glanzmann]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://eluveitie.ch/news/ |title=Archived copy |access-date=2018-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180304071133/http://eluveitie.ch/news/ |archive-date=2018-03-04 |url-status=dead }}</ref> The band has released 8 studio albums, 1 live album, 2 compilation albums, 11 official music videos, 9 singles and 1 demo.\n\n== Albums ==\n=== Studio albums ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:15em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"11\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Sales\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Swiss Hitparade|SWI]]<br /><ref name=\"Swiss Charts\">{{cite web|url=http://hitparade.ch/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Eluveitie|title=Swiss Charts}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[\u00d63 Austria Top 40|AUT]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://austriancharts.at/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Eluveitie|title=austriancharts.at / Eluveitie}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Canadian Albums Chart|CAN]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=eluveitie|cha