ple.com/us/album/evocation-i-arcane-dominion/id312694013 |archive-date=2014-08-22 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 20\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 195\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 60\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Everything Remains (As It Never Was)]]''\n|\n* Released: February 19, 2010\n* Label: Nuclear Blast\n* Formats: CD, CD+DVD, LP, digital download<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/everything-remains-as-it-never-was-bonus-track-version/353580037|title=Everything Remains As It Never Was (Bonus Track Version) by Eluveitie|publisher=|via=itunes.apple.com}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 8\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 22\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 31\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 110\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 19\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u2014\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 23\n|\n* US: 1,300+<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/eluveitie-everything-remains-first-week-sales-revealed/|title=ELUVEITIE: 'Everything Remains' First-Week Sales Revealed|first=|last=Blabbermouth|date=17 March 2010|website=BLABBERMOUTH.NET}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Helvetios]]''\n|\n* Released: February 10, 2012\n* Label: Nuclear Blast\n* Formats: CD, CD+DVD, LP, digital download<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/helvetios-exclusive-bonus-version/497249519|title=Helvetios (Exclusive Bonus Version) by Eluveitie|publisher=|via=itunes.apple.com}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 4\n| s