ence Olivier Awards]]\n| [[2010 Laurence Olivier Awards|Best Actress in a Supporting Role]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | ''[[The Misanthrope]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Evening Standard Theatre Awards]]\n| [[2010 Evening Standard Theatre Awards#Natasha Richardson Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2011\n| Empire Awards\n| [[Empire Hero Award]]\n|\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| 2012\n| Satellite Awards\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Actress \u2013 Motion Picture#Best Actress \u2013 Motion Picture (2011\u2013present)|Best Actress \u2013 Motion Picture]]\n| rowspan=\"5\" | ''[[Anna Karenina (2012 film)|Anna Karenina]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 2013\n| CinEuphoria Awards\n| Best Actress \u2013 International Competition\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| People's Choice Awards\n| [[39th People's Choice Awards#Movies|Favorite Dramatic Movie Actress]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| European Film Awards\n| European Actress\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Alliance of Women Film Journalists]]\n| Best Depiction of Nudity, Sexuality, or Seduction <br/> {{small|(shared with [[Aaron Taylor-Johnson]])}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Alliance of Women Film Journalists|Most Egregious Age Difference Between the <br/> Leading Man and the Love Interest]] <br/>{{small|(shared with [[Steve Carell]])}}\n| ''[[Seeking a Friend for the End of the World]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"12\" | 2014\n| Bra\u0219ov International Film Festival & Market\n| Best Actress\n| ''[[Anna Karenina (2012 film)|Anna Karenina]]''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Awards Circuit Community Awards\n| Best Actress in a Leading Role\n| rowspan=\"2\" | ''[[Begin Again (film)|Begin Again]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| International Online Cinema Awards (INOCA)\n| Best Actress\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Hollywood Film Awards]]\n| [[18th Hollywood Film Awards|Best Supporting Actress]]\n| rowspan=\"19\" | ''[[The Imitation Game]]''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| BIFA Awards\n| [[BIFA Award for Best Performance by an Actress in a British Independent Film#2010s|Best Actress]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[